==CantoMundo Poetry Prize== The organization has partnered with the [[University of Arkansas Press]] for an annual book prize. Edited by Deborah Paredez and Celeste Guzman, the first judge for the prize is celebrated poet [[Rafael Campo (poet)|Rafael Campo]].<ref name="uapress">{{cite web|url=http://www.uapress.com/cantomundopoetryseries/|publisher=uapress.com|title=CantoMundo Poetry Series|accessdate=2017-04-13}}</ref>
